cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CR, cs.MM

This paper is primarily focused on computer vision and machine learning techniques for face attribute detection. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of demographic information and transfer learning, which are common topics in machine learning and artificial intelligence, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) likely sub-categories as well. The paper also mentions privacy concerns, which could fall under the sub-category of cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). Finally, the paper uses datasets of images, which could also fall under the sub-category of cs.MM (Multimedia).
